description:
This Trans-Siberian Railroad map need Google Earth 5 to display correctly.
The kmz uses a significant amount of data from Hill's Trans-Siberian kmz, available at <a href="http://bbs.keyhole.com/ubb/ubbthreads.php?ubb=showflat&Number=29196&site_id=1#import">bbs.keyhole.com</a>.
It also uses the date libraries in <a href="http://js.fleegix.org/">Fleegix</a> to handle timezone conversions.
  thanks to both.

properties.description: All distances on the TSRR are given in kilometers (km) from Moscow.
